
# Log Analyzer Dashboard

A modular log analysis and threat detection system built using Python and Streamlit.

This project parses Apache-style web server logs, performs statistical analysis, detects suspicious activity, and visualizes results in a security monitoring dashboard.

---

##  Features

###  Log Analytics
- Total requests
- Top IP addresses
- Status code distribution
- Most requested endpoints
- Requests per minute timeline

### Threat Detection
- Brute-force login detection
- 404 reconnaissance detection
- High request rate detection

### Dashboard
- File upload interface
- Real-time visualization
- Security alert panel
- Clean dark monitoring UI

