## Installation

git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/log-analyzer-dashboard.git
cd log-analyzer-dashboard
pip install -r requirements.txt

---

## Run CLI Version

cd current
python main.py

---

##  Run Dashboard

cd current
streamlit run dashboard_streamlit/app.py

---

## Versions

* **v1.0** – CLI Log Analyzer
* **v2.0** – Streamlit Dashboard with Time-Based Analytics
* **v3.0** – Threat Detection Engine with Visual Alerts

---

## Project Purpose

This project simulates a simplified Security Operations Center (SOC) monitoring system.
It demonstrates log parsing, anomaly detection, backend modularity, and dashboard visualization.

---

